output.esnlc_DocTitleAnnotation: Priya Hajela is a fiction writer based in Pune. Writing is a second career for her. She graduated with an MFA in Creative Writing from Goddard College in Vermont in July 2017. Prior to taking to writing about five years ago, Priya worked at a variety of telecom and IT organizations in marketing and business development. input.esnlc_DocTitleAnnotation: Priya Hajela is a fiction writer based in Pune. Writing is a second career for her. She graduated with an MFA in Creative Writing from Goddard College in Vermont in July 2017. Prior to taking to writing about five years ago, Priya worked at a variety of telecom and IT organizations in marketing and business development. She began her career after an MBA from Vanderbilt University in 1992. Priya lives in Pune with her husband, and two little dogs. Her son is a young journalist based in Raleigh NC and her daughter studies in Costa Rica. One of Priya’s short stories (The Affair) was recently published in Indian Ruminations Magazine.
